@Add an rc script for nginx too
@
text
@Documentation on nginx can be found on the wiki:
	http://wiki.nginx.org/

You may want to put the following into your /etc/rc.local:

# start nginx
if [ -x ${PREFIX}/sbin/nginx ]; then
	echo -n ' nginx'; ${PREFIX}/sbin/nginx
fi
@


